1
00:00:16,975 --> 00:00:18,185
Stay away! Stay away!

2
00:00:18,852 --> 00:00:19,978
No!

3
00:00:24,775 --> 00:00:26,443
Stop! Stop!

4
00:00:39,289 --> 00:00:41,041
I can't take this anymore!

5
00:00:42,709 --> 00:00:46,838
This is a living hell!

6
00:00:52,678 --> 00:00:53,929
<i>Someone!</i>

7
00:00:54,012 --> 00:00:55,389
<i>Someone!</i>

8
00:00:57,849 --> 00:00:58,684
<i>Anyone!</i>

9
00:00:59,518 --> 00:01:02,437
{\an8}<i>Anyone… Save me… from this hell!</i>

10
00:01:02,521 --> 00:01:04,273
{\an8}Well…

11
00:01:04,773 --> 00:01:08,902
Compared to the office,
that would be heaven.

12
00:01:13,323 --> 00:01:15,951
{\an8}Oh, no…

13
00:01:16,493 --> 00:01:20,205
I need to sleep, since tomorrow's…

14
00:01:25,794 --> 00:01:27,337
Tomorrow…

15
00:01:28,964 --> 00:01:30,549
I got work again

16
00:01:31,508 --> 00:01:33,051
tomorrow?

17
00:01:36,722 --> 00:01:37,973
Work…

18
00:01:42,102 --> 00:01:45,731
I don't wanna go…

19
00:01:46,773 --> 00:01:48,817
<i>It happened three years ago.</i>

20
00:01:48,900 --> 00:01:49,735
Here.

21
00:01:49,818 --> 00:01:55,032
Starting today, you're assigned
to the Production Department…

22
00:01:55,115 --> 00:01:56,241
All right.

23
00:01:58,535 --> 00:02:02,789
My name is Akira Tendo.
Nice to meet you all!

24
00:02:02,873 --> 00:02:05,000
-Nice to meet you!
-Welcome aboard.

25
00:02:05,083 --> 00:02:07,044
<i>On my first day, I got the impression</i>

26
00:02:07,127 --> 00:02:09,504
<i>that it was a lively company</i>
<i>with a great atmosphere.</i>

27
00:02:09,588 --> 00:02:12,257
Yes! I'm happy to be here!

28
00:02:12,841 --> 00:02:16,553
<i>I landed a job in a production company</i>
<i>and industry I'd dreamed about.</i>

29
00:02:16,637 --> 00:02:20,015
<i>I was full of hopes, dreams, and ambition.</i>

30
00:02:20,682 --> 00:02:23,518
<i>I'm gonna pump out commercials</i>
<i>for all the big players!</i>

31
00:02:24,645 --> 00:02:27,272
<i>Which means</i>
<i>maybe I'll even meet some stars!</i>

32
00:02:27,981 --> 00:02:30,275
<i>Wow… I'm gonna do my best.</i>

33
00:02:30,359 --> 00:02:31,193
All right…

34
00:02:31,276 --> 00:02:32,986
You'll be sitting here.

35
00:02:33,070 --> 00:02:33,904
Yes, sir!

36
00:02:33,987 --> 00:02:37,324
If there's anything you don't understand,
ask Kosugi, the Department Chief.

37
00:02:37,407 --> 00:02:38,492
Nice to meet you!

38
00:02:38,575 --> 00:02:40,243
Yes! I look forward to working with you!

39
00:02:40,327 --> 00:02:42,120
Thank you for your hard work, sir.

40
00:02:45,332 --> 00:02:46,249
I'm sorry!

41
00:02:46,333 --> 00:02:47,584
It's all right.

42
00:02:47,667 --> 00:02:49,795
I wasn't looking where I was going…

43
00:02:49,878 --> 00:02:52,964
No! It's my…

44
00:03:05,185 --> 00:03:06,186
Excuse me!

45
00:03:06,269 --> 00:03:07,104
Here!

46
00:03:07,187 --> 00:03:08,355
Thank you.

47
00:03:08,438 --> 00:03:09,314
Sure…

48
00:03:09,398 --> 00:03:12,818
Nice to meet you.
I'm Saori Ohtori from Accounting.

49
00:03:12,901 --> 00:03:15,028
Looking forward
to working with you, Tendo.

50
00:03:16,655 --> 00:03:19,449
Same… here.

51
00:03:19,574 --> 00:03:24,663
For invoices or if you have any questions,
come ask me anytime.

52
00:03:24,746 --> 00:03:27,499
I sit right through there and to the left.

53
00:03:27,582 --> 00:03:28,959
Got it.

54
00:03:29,042 --> 00:03:32,295
Well, good luck on your first day!

55
00:03:37,092 --> 00:03:38,176
<i>She's so cute…</i>

56
00:03:38,885 --> 00:03:40,554
TORIYA

57
00:03:41,304 --> 00:03:43,140
Cheers!

58
00:03:43,223 --> 00:03:45,183
-Thanks for all your hard work!
-Bottoms up!

59
00:03:45,267 --> 00:03:46,893
Tendo, where did you go to school?

60
00:03:46,977 --> 00:03:47,811
K University!

61
00:03:47,894 --> 00:03:49,855
Wow, that's a good school!

62
00:03:49,938 --> 00:03:51,273
It's not really…

63
00:03:51,356 --> 00:03:52,232
Got a girlfriend?

64
00:03:52,315 --> 00:03:54,443
No, I haven't had any luck…

65
00:03:54,860 --> 00:03:57,028
